data.description: Come and see this Nicely Updated Affordable Townhome that is centrally located between Silverdale & Bremerton. Close to Bangor & Naval Shipyard. Near Buses, College, Schools, Highway 303 and Shopping within walking distance. Eat-in Kitchen Island and Dining area open to Great Room with access to a Private treed back Deck, with Roomy Shed. Covered Parking right in front. Newly Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring on main level. New updated Light fixtures. Laundry area and 2 bedrooms are located on upper level. All appliances included. Pets are welcome in this development! Low HOA dues include Common Area Maintenance, Lawn Service, Road Maintenance.
